t invests in public equity markets across the globe the firm invests in value stocks of small to midcap companies it employs fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to make its investments the firm makes inhouse research to make its investments speece tho speece thorson capital group inc is an employee owned investment manager the firm primarily provides its services to individuals including high net worth individuals pension and profit sharing plans and charitable organizations it also caters to pooled investment vehicles and state and municipal government entities the firm manages separate client focused equity portfolios along with an investment vehicle it invests in public equity markets across the globe the firm invests in value stocks of small to midcap companies it employs fundamental analysis with a bottomup stock picking approach to make its investments the firm makes inhouse research to make its investments speece thorson capital group inc was founded in  and is based at minneapolis minnesota detailed description  south sixth streetsuite minneapolis mn united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwstcapitalcom key executives for speece thorson capital group inc mr fred h speece jr cofounder chief compliance officer and director mr kenneth john thorson cofounder and director mr paul e pender cfa director age  mr benjamin david johnson cfa director mr matthew j weight cfa compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global marke